\c 4
\s Machinda aSoromoni nefuma yake
\p
\v 1 Zvino mambo Soromoni wakava mambo pamusoro paIsraeri wose.
\v 2 Zvino awa ndiwo machinda aaiva nawo: Azariya mwanakomana waZadhoki waiva mupristi;
\v 3 Erihorefi naAhija vanakomana vaShisha\x + 2 Sam. 8.17. 20.25. 1 Makor. 18.16.\x* vaiva vanyori; Jehoshafati mwanakomana waAhirudhi waiva munyori wenhoroondo;
\v 4 naBhenaya mwanakomana waJehoyadha waiva pamusoro pehondo\x + 2.35. 2 Sam. 8.18.\x*; naZadhoki naAbhiatari vaiva vapristi\x + 2.27. 2 Sam. 20.25.\x*;
\v 5 naAzariya mwanakomana waNatani waiva pamusoro pevatariri\x + 4.7,19,27. 5.16. 9.23. 22.47. 2 Makor. 8.10.\x*; naZabhudhi mwanakomana waNatani waiva mupristi\x + 4.2. 2 Sam. 8.18. 20.26.\x*, shamwari yamambo\x + 2 Sam. 15.37.\x*.
\v 6 Abhishari waiva pamusoro peimba; naAdhoniramu mwanakomana waAbhidha waiva pamusoro pemutero\x + 12.18. 5.14. 2 Sam. 20.24. 2 Makor. 10.18.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Zvino Soromoni waiva nevatariri gumi nevaviri pamusoro paIsraeri wose, vaitsvakira mambo neimba yake zvekudya; mwedzi pagore waiva paumwe neumwe kutsvaka zvekudya\x + 4.7,19,27. 5.16. 9.23. 22.47. 2 Makor. 8.10.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino awa mazita avo: Bheni-Huri pamakomo aEfuremu\x + Josh. 24.33.\x*;
\v 9 Bheni-Dhekeri paMakazi, nepaSharibhimi\x + Vato. 1.35. 2 Sam. 23.32.\x*, neBheti-Shemeshi\x + Josh. 19.22,38.\x*, neEroni-Bheti-Hanani;
\v 10 Bheni-Hesedhi paArubhoti; iye waiva neSokoho\x + 1 Sam. 17.1. Josh. 15.35,48.\x*, nenyika yose yeHeferi\x + Josh. 12.17.\x*;
\v 11 Bheni-Abhinadhabhi \add pa\add*nyika yose yeDhori\x + Josh. 11.2.\x*; Tafati mukunda waSoromoni waiva mukadzi wake;
\v 12 Bhaana mwanakomana waAhirudhi\x + 4.3.\x* \add pa\add*Taanaki\x + Vato. 5.19.\x*, neMegidho\x + Vato. 5.19.\x*, neBheti-Sheani\x + Josh. 17.11.\x* rose, iri paZaretani\x + Vato. 7.22.\x* pazasi peJezireeri\x + Josh. 17.16.\x*, kubva paBheti-Sheani\x + Josh. 17.11.\x* kusvika paAbheri-Mehora\x + Vato. 7.22.\x* kusvika mhiri kweJokimeami\x + 1 Makor. 6.68. Josh. 19.11.\x*;
\v 13 Bheni-Gebheri paRamoti-Giriyadhi\x + 22.3.\x*; waiva nemisha yaJairi mwanakomana waManase, yaiva paGiriyadhi\x + Num.. 32.41.\x*; iye waiva nedunhu reArigobhi\x + Det. 3.4. 2 Makor. 8.5.\x* iri paBhashani, maguta makuru makumi matanhatu aiva nemasvingo ane mazariro endarira\x + Det. 3.4. 2 Makor. 8.5.\x*;
\v 14 Ahinadhabhi mwanakomana waIdho \add pa\add*Mahanaimu\x + 1 Makor. 27.21.\x*;
\v 15 Ahimaazi paNafutari\x + 2 Sam. 15.27.\x*; iyewo wakatora Bhasemati mukunda waSoromoni kuva mukadzi;
\v 16 Bhaana mwanakomana waHushai paAsheri nepaAroti\x + 2 Sam. 15.37.\x*;
\v 17 Josafati mwanakomana waParua paIsasikari;
\v 18 Shimei mwanakomana waEra paBhenjamini\x + 1.8.\x*;
\v 19 Gebheri mwanakomana waUri panyika yeGiriyadhi, nyika yaSihoni mambo weVaAmori neyaOgi mambo weBashani; uye waiva iye oga mutariri waiva panyika iyo\x + Det. 3.8-10.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Judha naIsraeri vaiva vazhinji sejecha riri pagungwa pauwandu, vachidya, vachinwa, vachifara\x + 4.29. 3.8. Gen.. 22.17. 2 Makor. 1.9.\x*.
\v 21 Zvino Soromoni wakatonga pamusoro peushe hwose\x + 2 Makor. 9.26. Map. 72.8.\x* kubva parwizi \add kusvika\add* kunyika yeVaFirisitia\x + Gen.. 15.18.\x* nekusvika kumuganhu weEgipita; vakauya nezvipo uye vaishandira Soromoni mazuva ose eupenyu hwake\x + Map. 72.10. 1 Sam. 10.27.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Zvino zvekudya zvaSoromoni zvezuva rimwe zvaiva zviyero makumi matatu zveupfu hwakatsetseka, nezviyero makumi matanhatu zveupfu,
\v 23 nzombe gumi dzakakodzwa, nemombe makumi maviri dzekumafuro, nemakwai zana, kunze kwenondo\x + Det. 12.15.\x*, nemhara\x + Det. 12.15.\x*, nemhembwe\x + Det. 14.5.\x*, neshiri dzakakodzwa.
\v 24 Nokuti wakatonga pamusoro pechekuno kose kwerwizi, kubva paTifisa\x + 2 Madz. 15.16.\x* kusvika paGaza\x + Gen.. 10.19. Josh. 15.47.\x*, pamusoro pemadzimambo ose nechekuno kwerwizi; uye wakava nerugare kunhivi dzake dzose dzaiva dzakapoteredza\x + 1 Makor. 22.9.\x*.
\v 25 Zvino Judha naIsraeri vakagara pakadzivirirwa, umwe neumwe pazasi pemuzambiringa wake\x + Mik. 4.4. 2 Madz. 18.31. Isa. 36.16. Zek. 3.10.\x* nepazasi pemuonde wake, kubva paDhani kusvika paBheeri-Shebha, mazuva ose aSoromoni\x + 2 Sam. 3.10.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Soromoni waiva nezvidyiro zvuru makumi mana zvemabhiza engoro dzake, nevatasvi vemabhiza zvuru gumi nezviviri\x + 10.26. 2 Makor. 1.14. 2 Makor. 9.25. Det. 17.16.\x*.
\v 27 Zvino vatariri ava vaitsvakira mambo Soromoni zvekudya, newose waiswedera patafura yamambo Soromoni, umwe neumwe pamwedzi wake; havana kusiya kuchishaikwa chinhu\x + 4.5.\x*.
\v 28 Bhariwo* nemajanga emabhiza nemabhiza aimhanyisa vakauisa panzvimbo ya\add zvaifanira\add* kuva, umwe neumwe sezvaakatongerwa.
\p
\v 29 Mwari ndokupa Soromoni njere nekunzwisisa kukuru kwazvo\x + 3.12.\x*, neupamhi hwemoyo, sejecha riri pamahombekombe egungwa\x + 4.20.\x*.
\v 30 Zvino njere dzaSoromoni dzakapfuura njere dzevose vanakomana vemabvazuva\x + Vato. 6.3.\x*, nedzakapfuura njere dzose dzeVaEgipita\x + Mab. 7.22. Isa. 19.11.\x*.
\v 31 Nokuti waiva akachenjera kupfuura vanhu vose\x + 3.12.\x*; kupfuura Etani\x + 1 Makor. 6.44. 15.17,19. Map. 89.\x* muEzirahi\x + 1 Makor. 2.6.\x*, naHemani\x + 1 Makor. 2.6. 1 Makor. 6.33. 15.17,19. 25.1,4,5,6. Map. 88.\x*, naKarikori\x + 1 Makor. 2.6.\x*, naDharidha, vanakomana vaMahori; uye zita rake rakava kundudzi dzose dzaiva dzakapoteredza.
\v 32 Zvino wakataura tsumo zvuru zvitatu\x + Zvir. 1.1. Mup. 12.9.\x*, uye nziyo dzake dzaiva churu neshanu.
\v 33 Zvino wakataura zvemiti, kubva pamusidhari uri paRebhanoni\x + Vato. 9.15.\x* kusvika pamuhisopi unobuda parusvingo\x + Eki. 12.22.\x*; akataurawo zvemhuka, nezveshiri, nezvezvinokambaira, nezvehove.
\v 34 Zvino kwakasvika kubva kumarudzi ose kuzonzwa kuchenjera kwaSoromoni, kubva kumadzimambo ose enyika vakanzwa zvekuchenjera kwake\x + 10.1. 2 Makor. 9.23.\x*.